objectives.en:
The course introduces principles of evidence-based pubcli health / health practice.
Specifically: 
1. Define evidence-based public health and become familiar with key concepts in evidence-based public health;
2. Become familiar with key methods (incl study designs) for producing evidence for public health practice;
3. Apply key concepts to searching and evaluating the public health literature.

